GUYSSSS DON’T BE WORRIED! There are many reasons why this isn’t such a big deal. Many of you are worried. This video was a simple joke. You should be careful still though. If you follow the precautions then you are most likely not going to get it. If you live in china or somewhere with high numbers then you could be worried. However, even if you do get it, you WON’T die so really it isn’t that big of a deal. Its really similar to a common flu. Only difference is this is highly contagious and there is no cure YET. These are the reasons:
1. Very little people have died from it.
2. They are working on a cure and vaccine.
3. Media is just making it look big but this virus only seems really scary because it is spreading quickly.
4. There are many other deadly viruses other than this, more deadly than this, and have not wiped out humanity. So there is no way that this virus will.
5. Most people who are infected with is are old people but kids don’t really get it since they have a good immunity system.
